              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Activation"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "   One set of the monitors was attached to each",
                "         Cd sample."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GE",
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  The gamma rays from the monitors and Cd",
                " samples were measured by a high resolution Ge detec-",
                " tor which performance was characterized by a relative",
                " efficiency of 25 % to a 7.6cm*7.6cm diam. NaI(Tl)",
                " detector and an energy resolution of 2.0 keV full",
                " width at half-maximum (FWHM) at the 1.33MeV peak of",
                " 60Co. The peak detection efficiencies were determined",
                " with 152Eu and 60Co sources."
              ]
            }
          ],
