                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.9827
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                ".A set of 197Au/Al, 59Co/Al alloy wires, and Mo wire",
                " were used to monitor the neutron fluxes."
              ]
            }
          ],
